{
  "stem": "11133.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have school, so there was more time to play, more time to visit with other people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At first, it wasn't so bad, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, for a child.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For the grown ups, it must have been terrible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, when I think about it, now that I'm a parent, it must have been hard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did your parents work at that time?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They continued working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Both my mother then, at that point, joined-- the HoGo factory was taken over, was given to a person named Madritsch.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it became slowly turned from making shirts into making army uniforms for the Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's sort of a parallel to Schindler making-- you know, enameled pots and pans, then becoming-- making mess kits.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Madritsch then took over, and then my mother and my father both worked for Madritsch in the-- in the office.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father ran the factory, because he sort of knew it-- he was, you know, in terms of accounting and being able to predict how to make money out of it, I guess.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother worked in the office taking care of the books.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just sort of hung around, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was all alone, really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They left the ghetto to go to work, and I was left behind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which, I'm sure, must have been very difficult for my parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, as things progressed and got worse and worse in the ghetto-- as they, you know, made the ghetto smaller by transporting people out of the ghetto, and at that point, we didn't know where they were transporting them, you know, except someplace.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As the ghetto got smaller and smaller, it became evident that-- at least for my parents-- that the best thing would be for me to go out with them to work.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
